# The site was live under the old shape, so every address it published still
# has to land somewhere sensible. 301 rather than 302: these moves are final.
#
# Cloudflare matches the requested path LITERALLY, so /about and /about/ are
# two different sources and both have to be written. The old site canonicalised
# to the trailing slash — habibsaleh.com/about 308s to /about/ — so the slashed
# rule is the one that carries every real inbound link. Listing only the
# slashless form, as this file first did, would have 404'd /about/ outright and
# dropped all four project deep links onto the contents page.
#
# The specific rules must come before the splats, or /work/colored-air/ would
# be swallowed by /work/*.

# The two movements kept their own openings.
/work/colored-air             /read/colored-air/                                 301
/work/colored-air/            /read/colored-air/                                 301
/work/before-it-disappears    /read/before-it-disappears/                        301
/work/before-it-disappears/   /read/before-it-disappears/                        301

# The two garden projects are now stories read inside Colored Air, so their
# old addresses land on the leaf that announces them.
/work/season-of-the-mulberry  /read/colored-air/story-the-season-of-the-mulberry/ 301
/work/season-of-the-mulberry/ /read/colored-air/story-the-season-of-the-mulberry/ 301
/work/when-roses-bloom        /read/colored-air/story-when-roses-bloom/           301
/work/when-roses-bloom/       /read/colored-air/story-when-roses-bloom/           301

# The index of projects is now the contents of the book.
/work                         /contents/                                         301
/work/                        /contents/                                         301
/work/*                       /contents/                                         301

# The commercial wing was renamed but kept its slugs.
/editorial                    /commissions/                                      301
/editorial/                   /commissions/                                      301
/editorial/*                  /commissions/:splat                                301

# The essays became the notebook, slugs unchanged.
/writing                      /notebook/                                         301
/writing/                     /notebook/                                         301
/writing/*                    /notebook/:splat                                   301

# The about page became the colophon.
/about                        /colophon/                                         301
/about/                       /colophon/                                         301
